{{ define "title" }}
Periods
{{ end }}

{{ define "content" }}
<section class="intro">
<p>
Periods are timetable slots. Each course must have one unique period.
No student may choose more than one course per period.
</p>
<p>
Some example periods include
&ldquo;Monday/Wednesday CCA 1&rdquo;,
&ldquo;Tuesday/Thursday CCA 2&rdquo;,
etc.
</p>
<p>
On this page you may define a set of periods up-front;
in the courses tab, you may reference these periods.
</p>
</section>
<section class="listing">
<h2>Current periods</h2>
<div class="cards-grid">
{{ range . }}
<article class="card">
<header class="card-header">{{ . }}</header>
<details>
<summary>Actions</summary>
<form method="POST" action="/admin/periods/delete" class="stack-form">
<input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{ . }}" />
<div class="form-actions">
<button type="submit">Delete</button>
</div>
</form>
</details>
</article>
{{ end }}
</div>
</section>
<section class="new">
<h2>New period</h2>
<form method="POST" action="/admin/periods/new" class="stack-form">
<div class="form-field">
<label for="id">ID</label>
<input type="text" id="id" name="id" required />
</div>
<div class="form-actions">
<button type="submit">Add</button>
</div>
</form>
</section>
{{ end }}
